{"tid":676774,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[是日晚餐] 南蠻雞扒三文治","createTime":"2018-05-24T15:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T11:41:10.000Z","uid":43041,"like":43,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"139d32326391f80c7c38df6518420178709855f3","tid":676774,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"今日整左三文治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟個日本youtube channel整既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/231228_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F231228_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=193d761f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/231233_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F231233_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7635d95f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n豉油 湯 味琳 酒 白醋 水<br />\n攪埋一齊變成醬料擺埋一邊<br />\n鹽黑椒灑上雞扒度<br />\n再上太白粉&hellip; 不過我無所以用粟粉代替<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/231700_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F231700_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2d6aced8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拍走肉上面多餘既粉<br />\n煎到變色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/232529_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F232529_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=815868b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倒入醬料 反兩野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/232646_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F232646_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e09600fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n閂蓋 焗五分鐘或以上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/232912_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F232912_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e560a8d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n焗既同時 切好蔬菜同蕃茄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/232949_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F232949_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=631d1ee8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/233052_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F233052_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3422c22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鋪好菜同雞肉就差唔多食得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/233136_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F233136_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=15fa6c31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n包好保鮮紙，食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾好食，算成功啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食譜係度：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/97Y3euRUzZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F97Y3euRUzZ4&d=XH6AhjTccanxsmHwaXTVEAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3e0083ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/97Y3euRUzZ4</a>"},{"pid":"3a78bf969fe2f0f193cf92bd70adc94fde1e8ca8","tid":676774,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:38:40.000Z","msg":"好正呀屌....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似好易整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e04756244667b55a8799346f450f1c133232893","tid":676774,"uid":115238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:38:54.000Z","msg":"係咪MASA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7de66e5a8a6359e18c0eded99c948b412a4d0c","tid":676774,"uid":43041,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:38:58.000Z","msg":"屌拿星錯link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QDXk0SYyagg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQDXk0SYyagg&d=XH6AhjTccanxsmHwaXTVEAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=42948661\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QDXk0SYyagg</a><br />\n依個先係"},{"pid":"28416ee28fca06b4d71ee33efeeaf4cc0e744d63","tid":676774,"uid":96182,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"【葡萄適 &bull; 隨你點玩】 2018全新廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1edac4015108c0c83a81fb16b186f64c64979280","tid":676774,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e04756244667b55a8799346f450f1c133232893","tid":676774,"uid":115238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:38:54.000Z","msg":"係咪MASA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}